Sentencas: Cathode materials La2-xSrxNiO4 (LSN) for ITSOFC (intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell) were prepared by glycine-nitrate process (GNP).

Sentencas: The results show that no reaction occurrs between the electrode and the Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.9 (CGO)electrolyte at 1 100 degrees C and the electrode forms good contact with the electrolyte after sintering at 1 100 degrees C for 2 h.
